 Hydras nodded, "Your names are known to me..you will be a great addition to 
our team please enter the base. As for you Silverbolt and tankor is it? 
Please join us as well...for the more predacons we have the more our chances 
of completely destroying the maximals are. Follow us if you wish." Hydras 
turns. His Black wings spread out slightly his nonflamable cape blew in the 
wind. He headed towards the bridge.
